The Cell Phone Cinema Project

Project by Professor John Hunter and Mr. Justin Eyster at Bucknell University, 
Lewisburg, Pennsylvania, USA.

Project undertaken in 2015.

All source code written by Justin Eyster.

When complete, this program will provide functionality to search keywords or
phrases within a database of movie/tv closed captions and subtitles. This 
program will return lines containing instances of the specified keyword/phrase, 
along with metadata information about the movies containing the keyword/phrase.

For academic & educational purposes.